data.chText: （在2月14日常匿名寄送的）圣瓦伦廷节情人卡
data.enText: a card that you send to sb that you love on St Valentine's Day (14 February), often without putting your name on it

data.chText: （收受圣瓦伦廷节贺卡的）情人
data.enText: a person that you send a valentine to

word_means: (在2月14日常匿名寄送的)圣瓦伦廷节情人卡

means: (在2月14日常匿名寄送的)圣瓦伦廷节情人卡
(收受圣瓦伦廷节贺卡的)情人

tr: a sweetheart chosen to receive a greeting on Saint Valentine's Day

value.def: A valentine or a valentine card is a greetings card that you send to someone who you are in love with or are attracted to, usually without signing your name, on St Valentine's Day, the 14th of February.

trans: 情人节贺卡；情人节卡片
